  },
  "name": "sync-candidate-data-between-ats-and-hris-systems",
  "description": "n8n workflow template from ritik-prog/n8n-automation-templates-5000: sync-candidate-data-between-ats-and-hris-systems",
  "category": "Data",
  "tags": [
    "n8n advance",
